e-31524.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Ruined his face": Looksmaxxing streamer Clavicular brutally roasted after unrecognizable surgery reveal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131646532.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Looksmaxxing influencer Clavicular is facing heavy backlash after revealing the results of his rhinoplasty online. Before-and-after photos of the surgery quickly went viral, with many fans claiming he “ruined his face” and lost the distinct look that made him famous. Others defended the transformation, arguing the results may still be affected by swelling. The controversy has also reignited criticism surrounding the extreme beauty standards and risky lifestyle promoted within the online looksmaxxing community.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ruined-his-face-looksmaxxing-streamer-clavicular-brutally-roasted-after-unrecognizable-surgery-reveal/articleshow/131646532.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ruined-his-face-looksmaxxing-streamer-clavicular-brutally-roasted-after-unrecognizable-surgery-reveal/articleshow/131646532.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131646532,imgsize-420604.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Erica was described as an emotional asset": Candace Owens keeps pressure on officials over controversial Erika Kirk email]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131646512.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens says she is intensifying her FOIA fight over a controversial White House Correspondents’ Dinner email that allegedly described Erika Kirk as an “emotional asset” shortly after a shooting incident. Owens claimed government departments initially rejected her request as too broad, prompting her team to submit a narrower version with specific names and dates. She also accused Andrew Colvett and others of misleading the public, insisting the leaked email is authentic and will eventually be verified.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erica-was-described-as-an-emotional-asset-candace-owens-keeps-pressure-on-officials-over-controversial-erika-kirk-email/articleshow/131646512.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erica-was-described-as-an-emotional-asset-candace-owens-keeps-pressure-on-officials-over-controversial-erika-kirk-email/articleshow/131646512.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131646512,imgsize-52308.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What really happened to Reckless Ben’s GoFundMe amid the missing LEGO collection controversy?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131646446.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The Bricks &amp; Minifigs and Reckless Ben dispute began with claims that a $200,000 Star Wars LEGO collection was never returned to the Mansell family. The controversy later expanded into arrests, public accusations, lawsuits, store closures, and a major fundraising campaign. The latest development saw the Mansell GoFundMe page restored, while the legal battle continues ahead of a scheduled June 30 hearing.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-really-happened-to-reckless-bens-gofundme-amid-the-missing-lego-collection-controversy/articleshow/131646446.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-really-happened-to-reckless-bens-gofundme-amid-the-missing-lego-collection-controversy/articleshow/131646446.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T04:26:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131646443,imgsize-437544.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Are PlaqueBoyMax and Huda dating? Love Island USA star fuels fresh rumours with streamer]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131644479.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[PlaqueBoyMax and Huda Mustafa have sparked dating rumors after appearing together in livestreams, music sessions, gym posts, and social media content. The speculation grew following Huda’s breakup with Louis Russell. However, neither creator has confirmed a relationship. For now, publicly available information points to a close friendship and successful creative partnership rather than a confirmed romance.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/are-plaqueboymax-and-huda-dating-love-island-usa-star-fuels-fresh-rumours-with-streamer/articleshow/131644479.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/are-plaqueboymax-and-huda-dating-love-island-usa-star-fuels-fresh-rumours-with-streamer/articleshow/131644479.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T03:06:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131644477,imgsize-664799.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[TheBurntPeanut finally reveals Fortnite crossover after weeks of rumors]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131644101.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular streamer TheBurntPeanut has confirmed his Fortnite collaboration, not as a skin, but as an exceptionally rare in-game Sprite companion.  This unique buddy, with a mere 1.5% drop rate, offers gameplay advantages like increased rewards, including Mythic weapons.  Players can extract and reuse the Sprite in future matches, even piloting mech skins.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/theburntpeanut-finally-reveals-fortnite-crossover-after-weeks-of-rumors/articleshow/131644101.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/theburntpeanut-finally-reveals-fortnite-crossover-after-weeks-of-rumors/articleshow/131644101.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T01:22:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131644097,imgsize-1151623.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Video of Jesse Ridgway portraying character with Down syndrome resurfaces after announcement]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131644245.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[YouTuber Jesse Ridgway faces renewed scrutiny. An old video showing him portraying a character with Down syndrome has resurfaced. This comes after Ridgway announced he and his wife terminated a pregnancy after their unborn child was diagnosed with Trisomy 21. The resurfaced clip, from his series 'The Devil Inside', depicts exaggerated mannerisms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/video-of-jesse-ridgway-portraying-character-with-down-syndrome-resurfaces-after-announcement/articleshow/131644245.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/video-of-jesse-ridgway-portraying-character-with-down-syndrome-resurfaces-after-announc